snippet.textDisplay: This was the one thing that Endeavor was lacking in order to surpass All Might. It's not that he couldn't catch up to him, it was that there was never any need to catch up to him. All Might carried all the world's worries and responsibilities on his back, leaving nothing to Endeavor. It is ironic, in a sense, that Endeavor never required strength to become number one, but the weight of being number one to become truly strong.
snippet.textOriginal: This was the one thing that Endeavor was lacking in order to surpass All Might. It's not that he couldn't catch up to him, it was that there was never any need to catch up to him. All Might carried all the world's worries and responsibilities on his back, leaving nothing to Endeavor. It is ironic, in a sense, that Endeavor never required strength to become number one, but the weight of being number one to become truly strong.
